statements.sql: select `typi_menulinks`.`id`, `typi_menulinks`.`parent_id`, `uri`, `locale`, `module_name` from `typi_menulinks` inner join `typi_menulink_translations` on `typi_menulinks`.`id` = `typi_menulink_translations`.`menulink_id` where `uri` != '' and `module_name` != '' and `status` = '1' order by `module_name` asc
